法官阻止尼克·卡特以诽谤罪反诉强奸指控者https://www.nme.com/news/music/judge-blocks-nick-carters-attempt-to-countersue-rape-accuser-for-defamation-3784077?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=judge-blocks-nick-卡特斯试图以诽谤罪反诉强奸指控者Liberty DunworthThu, 15 Aug 2024 13:07:38 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3784077 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>针对前后街男孩歌手的指控首次出现于 2022 年</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judge-blocks-nick-carters-attempt-to-countersue-rape-accuser-for-defamation-3784077">法官阻止尼克·卡特以诽谤罪反诉强奸指控者的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>拉斯维加斯的一名法官阻止了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-carter">尼克·卡特</a>以诽谤罪反诉一名强奸指控者的企图。</p><p>去年8月，一位名叫阿什利<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-faces-third-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3491442">·雷普(Ashley Repp)的女子对这位前后街男孩成员提起诉讼</a>，声称尼克在她15岁时强奸了她。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/nick-carter-third-sexual-assault-lawsuit-filed-1235403404/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>报道，她声称这些事件在一艘游艇上发生过多次，还有一次是在 2003 年卡特 23 岁的时候在一辆旅游巴士后面发生的。</p><p>尼克的律师在一份声明中称这些指控“荒谬”，称这些指控当时已接受调查，但被认为“毫无根据”而被拒绝。今年 1 月，卡特以诽谤罪反诉她，并声称雷普告诉他，她已经 18 岁了，而且性行为是“双方自愿的”。</p><p>然而，法官现已裁定驳回反诉讼。在周二的拉斯维加斯听证会上，法官小乔·哈迪（Joe Hardy Jr.）阻止了这一尝试，并（通过<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/nick-carter-sues-accuser-defamation-dismissed-1235080182/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em></a>）表示：“事实是绝对的辩护。根据卡特自己的司法供述，他们确实发生了性行为。他们发生了性关系，而且她还未成年。”</p><p>卡特首先被香农·露丝指控性侵犯，香农<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-accused-of-raping-17-year-old-fan-in-2001-3363992">·露丝于 2022 年对这位歌手提起民事诉讼</a>。她声称，2001 年，17 岁的她在华盛顿州塔科马举行后街男孩演唱会后，这位艺术家强奸了她。卡特的律师回应了这些指控，称这些指控“在法律上毫无依据”且“完全不真实”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784080" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784080" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784080" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="尼克·卡特 2024 年登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784080" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·卡特 (Nick Carter) 将于 2024 年登台表演。图片来源：Iwi Onodera/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>他还被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-sued-for-sexual-assault-by-dreams-melissa-schuman-3429104">指控袭击了 Dream 前成员梅丽莎·舒曼 (Melissa Schuman)</a> ，她最初于 2017 年向警方提交了报告。卡特对这些指控做出了回应，称他“感到震惊和悲伤”，因为他相信他们的遭遇是“双方自愿的”。</p><p>在诽谤诉讼提起两个月后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-files-countersuit-against-rape-accuser-3391785">他对露丝和舒曼提出反诉</a>。他的法律团队还指控露丝被舒曼“操纵做出虚假指控”。</p><p>大约在这个时候，雷普提出诉讼，指控这位歌手强奸。<br />周二（8 月 13 日），卡特反诉舒曼诽谤，索赔 250 万美元（195 万英镑），声称她发表有关他的言论“具体意图是损害卡特的声誉并干扰他的商业机会、优势和合同”。 <em><a href="https://people.com/nick-carter-sues-rape-accuser-melissa-schuman-alleges-she-intentionally-defamed-him-8695018" target="_blank" rel="noopener">每人</a></em>。</p><p>早在五月份，卡特还否认了一部名为<em>《堕落偶像：尼克和亚伦·卡特》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-hits-back-at-outrageous-sexual-assault-claims-3761061">的纪录片中针对他的“令人发指的”性侵犯指控</a>。</p><p>该项目指控这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/backstreet-boys">后街男孩</a>歌手在 00 年代初袭击了三名女性——露丝、舒曼和雷普。据报道，卡特拒绝参加该系列纪录片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784081" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784081" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784081" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-performs@2000x1270.jpg" alt="尼克·卡特 (Nick Carter) 将于 2024 年登台表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-performs@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-performs@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-performs@2000x127