ngblud-cameo-3784043">《Watch Sex Pistols》和 Frank Carter 在 Bush Hall 重聚演出中将歌词改为“God Save The Queen”（Yungblud 短暂客串）的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Little Simz 将于本月策划泰特现代美术馆深夜晚会https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-to-curate-evening-of-tate-modern-lates-this-month-3784059?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=little-simz-to-本月晚些时候的泰特现代艺术之夜策展Liberty DunworthThu, 15 Aug 2024 12:23:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3784059 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>当晚将包括对话、研讨会和 DJ 表演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-to-curate-evening-of-tate-modern-lates-this-month-3784059">Little Simz 本月策划泰特现代美术馆晚间晚会的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">小西姆兹 (Little Simz)</a>与泰特现代美术馆 (Tate Modern) 合作，将于本月策划一场晚会。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/little-simz-cover-interview-2021-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-3035532"><em>NME</em>大读物 – Little Simz：“很高兴看到我的同龄人获胜。当他们赢了，我就赢了”</a></strong></li></ul><p>此次合作将于本月最后一个星期六（8 月 31 日）举行，这位屡获殊荣的说唱歌手、歌手和演员将在伦敦画廊举办一场特别策划的音乐、研讨会和对话之夜。</p><p>这是该美术馆正在进行的泰特现代美术馆晚间系列活动的一部分，该系列活动让游客有机会参加一个免费的艺术、音乐、电影等晚会，“志同道合的人们可以在心中聚集在一起”伦敦的文化景观”。</p><p>八月底的一晚，这个独家之夜将由 Simz 亲自设计，她还将与广播公司 Clara Amfo 一起向参观者讲述她的灵感以及她与视觉艺术的关系。</p><p> “我非常高兴能够在泰特现代美术馆策划一个夜晚。这将是非常特别的，”这位说唱歌手在一份新的声明中说道。 “能够邀请各行各业的人们进入这个空间通过艺术进行联系是很强大的。我希望人们能从这次经历中受到启发、振奋和感动。” </p><figure id="attachment_3784064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Little Simz 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节第四天表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Little-Simz@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784064" class="wp-caption-text"> Little Simz 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节第四天表演。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>活动中，著名编舞家兼动作指导 Kloé Dean 将在 South Tank 举办独家舞蹈研讨会，他们还可以在随后由 Simz 选择的 DJ 表演中测试舞蹈动作。</p><p>富有远见的艺术家和舞台设计师 Es Devlin 也将亮相，在当晚的艺术聊天中谈论是什么激励了她，以及包括小说家 Caleb Azumah Nelson 和著名画家、滑板运动员和艺术家 Slawn 在内的其他主要创意人士。</p><p>当晚的其他活动包括由多学科艺术家和插画家 Fiona Quadri 主办的 Zine 研讨会，以及 JK 卡通工作室的 Jadore Nicholas 举办的卡通着色课程。</p><p>作家卡罗琳·阿德耶米 (Caroline Adeyemi) 将在泰特美术馆通过诗歌和散文释放内心的反思，游客还可以见到艺术家埃琳娜·奥伊曼 (Elena Ooijman)，并参加集体呼吸和运动课程。</p><p> Lates with Little Simz 于 8 月 31 日下午 6 点至晚上 10 点举行，免费入场，并可通过免费门票获得研讨会、对话等活动的门票。 <a href="https://www.tate.org.uk/whats-on/tate-modern/tate-modern-lates" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处了解更多信息</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784063" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784063" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784063" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270.jpg" alt="泰特现代美术馆布拉瓦尼克大楼的外景" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tate-modern@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784063" class="wp-caption-text">泰特现代美术馆布拉瓦尼克大楼的外景。图片来源：Mike Kemp/来自 Getty Images 的图片</figcaption></figure><p>就在宣布 Little Simz 与泰特现代美术馆合作的消息几天前，确认她将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-a-snippet-of-coldplays-new-single-we-pray-featuring-little-simz-3781687">出演 Coldplay 的新单曲“We Pray”（同样由 Burna Boy 主演）</a> 。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">克里斯·马丁</a>领导的乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-coldplay-debut-new-song-with-little-simz-3770358">第五次在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上展示这</a>首歌后，这首歌首次成